Dear users: First of all thank you for using Voicelator it really inspires us to work on improvements every day. The following update is no exception. We have improved some features in this version. Thank you for improving Voicelator with your continued support and feedback! Never lose the urge to share your impressions and comments with us. Contact us at support appvillis.com.

Hello everyone First update of 2020 yes! With each update Voicelator becomes more and more useful for those who want to understand and be understood everywhere. Here are some new features that will make it even easier to use: Phrasebook of the most common words and phrases in all languages Extensions mode to translate texts within any application or browser without closing any tab Bug fixes and performance improvement. Thank you for helping us improve Voicelator with your continued support and feedback! Don t miss the opportunity to share your impressions and comments with us: support appvillis.com.

Hello everyone We want to use these last hours of 2019 efficiently with a new update! Let s see what s under the Christmas tree: More input languages available for keyboard translation Real time voice recognition in all voice recording modes Bug fixes and performance improvement. Thank you for your comments and for your continued support! We are committed to making this app even better so don t miss the opportunity to share your impressions and comments with us: support appvillis.com. See you in 2020!

Thank you for choosing Voicelator! We re back with amazing news! Our designers have worked very hard to bring you a great design update. From now on you can understand others and others can understand you and with style! . Tap the bright icons enjoy the bright colors vibrant fonts and forget about the language barrier. We have also corrected some errors and improved the performance of the application so that you can carry out your translations quickly and easily. Thank you for your comments and for your continued support!
